CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Charlotte Parris...Laverne Butler, AKA sponsored...Harris Photos."Cutline of image published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 8, 1954, pg. 12 reads: "Who Will Be Crowned Teen-Queen Friday Night?  Gloria Bey Still in Lead With 1,707 Votes - LaVerne Butler"
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Charlotte Parris wearing dark short sleeve belted dress with light colored buttons and striped fabric trim, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Laverne Butler wearing sheer neck scarf and zigzag patterned sweater with dark ribbed cuffs and collar, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
